{"tid":1658930,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"Porto獨遊記","createTime":"2019-10-16T16:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T20:59:34.000Z","uid":296614,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"61712695b23aa59d5667196010374e1a49e728c2","tid":1658930,"uid":296614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:31:58.000Z","msg":"話說之前做嘢做到好大壓力好辛苦，又咁啱有一個禮拜假<br />\n決定掉自己去一個陌生嘅城市去體驗下<br />\n至於點解會揀Porto呢？<br />\n純粹因為㩒到平機票 同埋身邊有朋友去過都話好玩過Lisbon<br />\n所以就係咩都無plan過，對Porto一無所知嘅情況之下飛過去了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43JjYkx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43JjYkx.jpg&h=d1da5765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搭好早機幾乎成晚無瞓我未起飛已經瞓左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />醒左望出去就係呢個景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8DoFyU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8DoFyU.jpg&h=3b3df57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搭地鐵出去city center，嗰度啲地鐵好光猛好靚！<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n其實我第一次寫遊記㗎咋 希望有人睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0c6a87468112e1a13ef7b79b9f75c9da9ebaa8","tid":1658930,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:32:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ff864bda5d8e0ab8e70ce06837800dfe4b233bc4","tid":1658930,"uid":76159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"留名跟live"},{"pid":"c944b5864fdefa4761b738f4db7c8821aa1c770c","tid":1658930,"uid":49560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2a68940c6fb21daad47089c2e51dd1954546b298","tid":1658930,"uid":301762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:35:54.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"7c9d078ddfc03d00121a898ada13854738b0151d","tid":1658930,"uid":111493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:36:35.000Z","msg":"1個人backpacks ? <br />\n想知住宿方面"},{"pid":"f3df81c0dc7fe587b021241870db640492edeaa7","tid":1658930,"uid":296614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c9d078ddfc03d00121a898ada13854738b0151d","tid":1658930,"uid":111493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:36:35.000Z","msg":"1個人backpacks ? <br />\n想知住宿方面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"係呀 我都係住hostel咋 &euro;80到4晚"},{"pid":"8c70aa51f87a8ba08d1f8bef83aab9ffaac0fb7a","tid":1658930,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"lm，三個月前去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf221ba9870d359181eae07a8f76659492a6930","tid":1658930,"uid":248166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:26:33.000Z","msg":"7月去完，個陣有開post live, 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0744540a2a4d8f65caa645e29543d55c41716d","tid":1658930,"uid":248166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c70aa51f87a8ba08d1f8bef83aab9ffaac0fb7a","tid":1658930,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"lm，三個月前去完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57c2130ba669a125ab7ffac7bc26f9ee6c7ad5c","tid":1658930,"uid":305553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:27:44.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"f8b9b25fd99a5c87df760337e422258e744acce9","tid":1658930,"uid":296614,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"去到hostel放低行李之後就衝左出去食嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivDsnWO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivDsnWO.jpg&h=102117a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係傳說中全世界最靚嘅麥當勞！不過入面就同一般麥當勞無咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ATcs7wS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATcs7wS.jpg&h=bd73b6ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食飽之後就去呢到參加個local tour<br />\n啱晒我呢啲咩都無plan嘅遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次個tour guide係一個大學生叫Marie，佢帶我地同行15人行左Porto好多主要嘅景點，再講下Porto以前啲歷史，Marie講左好多關於佢地點樣推翻前總統Salazar，最出名當然就係康乃馨革命！<br />\n佢都會介紹一啲local經常去嘅餐廳！最重要係呢個tour係。免。費。㗎！（不過佢最尾都會問大家攞少少tips嘅，大家可以自己選擇比唔比，我最後都比左&euro;15因為我都好enjoy）<br />\n呢個tour係hostel介紹比我嘅，叫Porto Walkers<br />\n我地呢團有好多來自世界各地嘅遊客，近嘅有英國法國德國，甚至當地葡萄牙人都有，遠嘅就有美國加拿大（可能因為係英文tour，所以一個大陸人都無！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ApNdiHk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FApNdiHk.jpg&h=cf9a6dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTqqUfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTqqUfL.jpg&h=06ea1ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2wb5UfN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2wb5UfN.jpg&h=09863e29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VLAFH9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVLAFH9c.jpg&h=69e0a215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcFnb2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvcFnb2u.jpg&h=18b3f678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想講下呢幅圖，唔知大家有無留意到佢有咩特別呢？<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n答案就係呢個女神像係無矇眼㗎！傳統嘅Lady Justice係會矇眼代表法律係不徇私同一視同仁，但係呢個像係無矇眼就係象徵著葡萄牙改革之後法律已經改變，唔再受佢地極權政府嘅影響，會張開雙眼咁去審判！<br />\n我估呢個可能係全世界唯一一個唔矇眼嘅Lady Justice！"},{"pid":"a793180016bd963a7b454753f8534457b1013487","tid":1658930,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:05:41.000Z","msg":"直飛？ 貴唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baba9da1306d1102cf80a9654870eb55e46210b8","tid":1658930,"uid":296614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a793180016bd963a7b454753f8534457b1013487","tid":1658930,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:05:41.000Z","msg":"直飛？ 貴唔貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T18:31:18.000Z","msg":"我係倫敦飛過去嘅，來回應該&pound;100到 計埋行李加priority<br />\n香港好似無直飛去Porto？我都唔係好清楚"},{"pid":"a2b30dd7f7f76b6ebd3d91b99299b0a39d8fe9e4","tid":1658930,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:59:38.000Z","msg":"淨係去波圖唔去里斯本？"},{"pid":"41fab09bff3256dc55fa01c9d515b17cf649b659","tid":1658930,"uid":296614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2b30dd7f7f76b6ebd3d91b99299b0a39d8fe9e4","tid":1658930,"uid":197125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T19:59:38.000Z","msg":"淨係去波圖唔去里斯本？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T21:07:39.000Z","msg":"係啊"},{"pid":"b84282e18ad1c72938f44d2344935e54463108ea","tid":1658930,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T21:32:53.000Z","msg":"上年12月去完"},{"pid":"6adbecfbf7b4350343f294d2eeb137ffe7fe845a","tid":1658930,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T21:35:50.000Z","msg":"睇波5歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79434ba5ba377e10f36c636a1c88484b535e496","tid":1658930,"uid":326463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T21:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4dzO3J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4dzO3J.jpg