":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T21:35:50.000Z","msg":"睇波5歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"咁平？我本身都想去睇但係最後決定去搭tram影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:40:20.000Z","msg":"佢講緊葡乙咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef1683b42c765bb2bf520c5b49cc1efde3d6069","tid":1658930,"uid":296614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:16:00.000Z","msg":"Marie帶左我地去一個好靚嘅公園，個度可以望到Porto嘅全景。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9iPHs2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9iPHs2.jpg&h=d97a55bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果我同另一個英國嘅遊客掛住影相跟甩左Marie<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩我地行到下面呢條街之後見翻佢地！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0VD4whr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0VD4whr.jpg&h=e18a8761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來佢地成班去左食葡撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係葡萄牙傳統食法係會加肉桂粉係上面，再配埋espresso。仲有啲人會加Brandy落杯espresso到！<br />\n（不過我都係覺得呢舊無kfc嗰啲咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Ziwbht.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Ziwbht.jpg&h=28e3393f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行完個tour之後我就返返去Hostel，因為我報左名去食佢地嘅&euro;10葡萄牙晚飯！<br />\n嗰晚食左嗰葡式雞批同番茄飯！當然唔少得Porto嘅名物Port wine<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uj4vrQR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUj4vrQR.jpg&h=4394ccb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢餐飯都食得好開心，有大概10個都係係hostel住嘅tourists一齊食，都有唔少亞洲人（台灣韓國日本都有）。嗰晚我就識左個墨西哥女仔，最後發現原來我地係roommate<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a6fabbc05bf35804d2a318e2ad929dcd91e6c","tid":1658930,"uid":124262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo